System requirements:  
=================

Operating system: Windows Vista, 7, 8.1 +
Processor: 1.6 Ghz
Memory: 1 GB RAM
Video Card: Direct X 10 + Capable GPU
Free space on hard drive: 3 GB available space

Game information:  
=================

Established in the best tradition of the great hits Age of Empires
and Age of Kings, it is worthy of a place in the collection of any,
even the most advanced player! Nine absolutely different peoples,
each of them - the unique skills and talents over. Epic battles in
the atmosphere of ancient legends and tales. Here are fighting
even the ancient gods of Greece, Egypt and the Scandinavian
countries. After all, this is the era when the flow of blood is shed,
and people worship the great inhabitants of heaven. Era of myths
and legends!

Game Features:  
=================

The publication also includes the official continuation of the
game - The Titans. Players will take control of an entirely new
race and create the most destructive creature - a giant battle
of titanium! With his participation battle acquire, unprecedented
scope and sweep to the ground the enemy hordes became more
interesting and much more pleasant.Age of Mythology: Extended
Edition is an adapted version of the project under the current system.

The Extended Edition includes:

Age of Mythology
Age of Mythology: The Titans
Golden Gift Campaign.

Repack Features:  
=================

Age of Mythology: Extended Edition
Do not cut / recoded
Version of the game - v1.8.2722 (update 5)
Ability to select a combination of text  voice
